## Featherless LLM Client Pattern
```python
from openai import OpenAI

client = OpenAI(
    api_key=os.environ["FEATHERLESS_API_KEY"],
    base_url="https://api.featherless.ai/v1",
)

# Orchestrator ‚Äî strong reasoning model
ORCHESTRATOR_MODEL = "meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct"

# Seller research ‚Äî fast, efficient model
SELLER_MODEL = "meta-llama/Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct"

# Usage (same as OpenAI SDK):
response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model=ORCHESTRATOR_MODEL,
    messages=[{"role": "user", "content": "..."}],
)
```

For LangChain nodes, use `langchain-openai` with custom base_url:
```python
from langchain_openai import ChatOpenAI

llm = ChatOpenAI(
    model="meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct",
    api_key=os.environ["FEATHERLESS_API_KEY"],
    base_url="https://api.featherless.ai/v1",
)
```

